<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Refund Sales | Hamza Paints</title>
  <link rel="icon" href="/images/weldon-paints-logo.png" type="image/png">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/refundSales.css">
</head>

<body>

  <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

  <main>
    <div class="content-wrapper">
      <div class="form-wrapper">
        <h1>Refund Sales</h1>

        <!-- ✅ Info box — dokandar ko samjhao kya hoga -->
        <div style="background:#e8f5e9; border:1px solid #a5d6a7; border-radius:8px;
                    padding:12px 16px; margin-bottom:20px; font-size:13px; color:#2e7d32;">
          <strong>ℹ️ Refund Sales kaise kaam karta hai:</strong><br>
          • <strong>Cash sale:</strong> Poora paisa wapas karo customer ko , ya paiso kay badlay chez du<br>
          • <strong>Khata sale (Unpaid):</strong> Sirf khata kam hoga, kuch wapas nahi<br>
          • <strong>Khata sale (Partial Paid tha):</strong> Pehle khata kam hoga, phir jo zyada tha wo wapas karo , ya doosre bill mein adjust karo , ya badlay mai naye chez du<br>
          • <strong>Khata sale (Paid tha):</strong> Ya paisa customer ko wapas karo   , ya paiso ko dosray Khata mai adjust karo , ya phir enkay badlay naye chez du

        </div>

        <form id="refundForm" class="form-container">
          <input type="text" name="saleID" placeholder="Enter Sale ID" required />

          <input min="1" max="1000" type="number" name="productQuantity"
            placeholder="Enter Quantity of Sale" required />

          <!-- ✅ Tick wala checkbox bilkul hata diya — system khud calculate karta hai -->

          <button type="submit" id="add">Refund Now</button>
        </form>

        <div id="refundResult" style="margin-top:20px; font-size:16px;"></div>

        <!-- Paisa wapas box — running total -->
        <div id="cashReturnBox" style="display:none; margin-top:16px;
             background:#e8f5e9; border:1px solid #a5d6a7;
             border-radius:8px; padding:14px;">
          <p style="margin:0; font-size:15px; color:#1b5e20; font-weight:bold;">
            💵 Customer ko paisa wapas karo ya adjust karo:
            <span id="cashReturnAmount" style="font-size:18px;"></span>
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Session table -->
        <div id="refundTableSection" style="display:none; margin-top:30px;">
          <h3 style="margin-bottom:10px; color:#37474f; font-size:16px;">
            Refunded Items — Is Session Mein
          </h3>
          <div class="table-scroll">
            <table style="width:100%; border-collapse:collapse; font-size:13px;">
              <thead>
                <tr style="background:#37474f; color:#fff;">
                  <th style="padding:10px; text-align:left;">Sale ID</th>
                  <th style="padding:10px; text-align:left;">Brand</th>
                  <th style="padding:10px; text-align:left;">Item</th>
                  <th style="padding:10px; text-align:left;">Color</th>
                  <th style="padding:10px; text-align:left;">Unit</th>
                  <th style="padding:10px; text-align:center;">Sold Qty</th>
                  <th style="padding:10px; text-align:center;">Refund Qty</th>
                  <th style="padding:10px; text-align:right;">Rate</th>
                  <th style="padding:10px; text-align:right;">Wapas / Adjust</th>
                  <th style="padding:10px; text-align:center;">Status</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody id="refundTableBody"></tbody>
              <tfoot>
                <tr style="background:#eceff1;">
                  <td colspan="8"
                    style="padding:10px; text-align:right; font-weight:bold; color:#37474f;">
                    Total Wapas / Adjust:
                  </td>
                  <td style="padding:10px; text-align:right; font-weight:bold; color:#c62828;">
                    Rs. <span id="sessionGrandTotal">0.00</span>
                  </td>
                  <td></td>
                </tr>
              </tfoot>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <script src="/javascripts/refundSales.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
